
An android component is simply a piece of code that has a well defined life cycle e.g. Activity, Receiver, Service, Broadcast, contentProvider etc.

Content Provider
Content Providers are used to share data between the applications.

Service
Service is a background process that can run for a long time.

AndroidManifest.xml
It contains informations about activities, content providers, permissions etc

Broadcast Receivers 
simply respond to broadcast messages from other applications or from the system itself.(Notification)
